How to cite
----------------

Thibaut, Robin, & Maximilian Ramgraber. (2021). SKBEL - Bayesian Evidential Learning framework built on top of scikit-learn (v2.0.0). Zenodo. https://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6205242

